CAPE TOWN – iStore has announced that South Africans will be able to purchase the new Bluetooth Tile Mate tracker. It will be available at any iStore nationwide. The new Tile Mate and Tile Pro will have the replaceable battery that should last a year. The new tiles will also have extended Bluetooth range of up to 150 feet, up from 100 feet before, and the Pro reaches 300 feet compared to the previous 200 feet. Pricing:   Tile Premium covers an unlimited number of Tiles and users will receive six new features such as:   Users can sign up through their iOS app or the Tile website. An Android version is coming soon. You can also check out the iStore online to purchase the device. BUSINESS REPORT ONLINE